General.Name: Veris Ltd
General.Description: Veris Limited provides surveying and spatial data services primarily in Australia. The company provides an end-to-end spatial data solution, which includes data collection, analysis, interpretation, data hosting and access, modelling, and sharing and insights for clients. It also offers engineering survey; engineering and property services; and town planning and urban design services. It serves infrastructure, property, mining, resources, energy, utilities, government, and defence sectors. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is headquartered in East Melbourne, Australia.
